{"tid":1589030,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"話輸緊既入黎","createTime":"2019-09-23T05:40:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T05:44:21.000Z","uid":251071,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"77876bc86d294d16b472bcc2d9026628dfc055c1","tid":1589030,"uid":251071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T05:40:28.000Z","msg":"今次場運動同之前佔領唔同<br />\n你佔到佢回應你贏，你比佢清走你就輸<br />\n但今次佢清完你走，走完你又可以出返黎<br />\n其實只要我地一日唔肯完，場運動就會一直落去<br />\n所以如果會輸，都係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">輸自己</span><br />\n係輸比<span style=\"color: red;\">白色恐怖</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">灰心</span><br />\n但我地繼續玩落去，<br />\n佢地都好頭痕，而且都真係有好多影響<br />\nIf we burn, you burn with us<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港人，真係要加油</span>"},{"pid":"e424a23a6ea63305f7c907638ada6d5a86fe19ab","tid":1589030,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T05:42:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"9fbf5b61062c0f57e8992faadb50f3450e590868","tid":1589030,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T05:44:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}